    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-assessment-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped as not-assessed at MRL 2. Validation evidence (VR-01, VR-02) demonstrates NIH prediction error of 8.3% and shear stress agreement within 11%, both within acceptance thresholds. GCI < 3.2% confirms adequate discretization. The credibility package supports the regulatory claim that the CFD model is fit for purpose to identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. Decision: Accepted for submission to 510(k) regulatory dossier.",
